---
// Hero Component
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden pt-16 pb-24 lg:pt-24 lg:pb-32">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="z-10">
        <span class="inline-block py-1 px-3 rounded-full bg-primary/20 text-secondary font-bold text-xs tracking-wider uppercase mb-6 border border-primary/30">
          Logística Nacional en Chile
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold text-secondary leading-[1.1] mb-6">
          Transporte de Carga de <span class="text-primary">Arica</span> a <span class="text-primary">Punta Arenas</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
          Profesionalismo y seguridad en cada ruta. Ofrecemos soluciones logísticas integrales con monitoreo constante y cobertura en todo el territorio chileno.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href="/cotizar" class="bg-primary hover:bg-yellow-500 text-secondary px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-extrabold text-base transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined" aria-hidden="true">description</span>
            Solicitar Cotización
          </a>
          <a href="#servicios" class="border-2 border-secondary text-secondary hover:bg-secondary hover:text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-extrabold text-base transition-all text-center">
            Ver Servicios
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="absolute -top-12 -right-12 w-64 h-64 bg-primary/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border-4 border-white rotate-1">
          <img 
            src="/img/hero.jpg" 
            alt="Camión de carga MYR Transportes - Flota propia para envíos a todo Chile" 
            class="w-full h-[500px] object-cover"
            width="600"
            height="500"
          >
        </div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-6 -left-6 bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-xl flex items-center gap-4 border border-gray-100">
          <div class="bg-green-100 p-2 rounded-full">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-green-600" aria-hidden="true">verified</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-tighter">Estado de Carga</p>
            <p class="font-bold text-secondary">100% Monitoreado</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
